<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ṁgganāyāḥ Okkettugaṇḍaḥ patirāsarasyā rājēṁdracōḍāṁ<unclear>kkita</unclear> nāma
<lb n="2" break="no"/>dhēyaḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1*] tasya svasā <unclear>mē</unclear>ḍamacānināmā pitrōḥ phalāvāptikritē śakābde <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śarēṣu<unclear>khēṁ</unclear>ddupradhitēdhilōhadaṇḍadvayasthāpitadīpayugmaṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] Utta
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rāyaṇasaṁkrāṁttinimittēsma dadāti sā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Akhaṇḍaṁ bhīmanāthāya trilōkīgatakīrttayē [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 3*] śakavarṣa 105<unclear>4</unclear> nēṇḍu śrīmaccālukyavikrama
<lb n="4" break="no"/>saṁvatsa <unclear>5</unclear>7 gu śrāhi kolani Okkettugaṇḍaya celiyalu mēḍāsāni tama taṇḍridamatināyakunikiṁ dama <unclear>ta</unclear>lli prōlāsāniki<unclear>ṁ</unclear> dharmmavugā śrībhīmē
<lb n="5" break="no"/>śvaramahādēvaraku nuttarāyaṇasaṁkrāṁtti nimittamunaṁ beṭṭina yakhaṇḍavartti lōhadaṇḍu diviyalu reṇṭiki nācaṁdrārkkamu neyu sariyiṁcuvārugā
<lb n="6"/>bōlu nalvuruṁ būṁṭṭugā modaliyaḍapuna prōlabōla nāvani yaḍapuna Aytibōla kā<unclear>ṭa</unclear>ni vasamunaṁ beṭṭina modavulu 50 nāvabōla muppana vasamu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>naṁ beṭṭina modavulu 50 berasi I<unclear>nu</unclear>payeḍlu 100 ṇṭiki nityapaḍi pōyaṁkkala tribhuvanāṁkkusa nēti mānalu reṇḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> likhitaṁ peddanācā<unclear>ri</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
